00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:13,000
Come with me, quick. Something happened.

565
00:25:19,599 --> 00:25:20,519
You too, come with me quickly.

566
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:23,920
Hurry.

567
00:25:27,359 --> 00:25:28,039
I brought them all.

568
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:30,079
Okay.

569
00:25:31,039 --> 00:25:31,640
Everyone's here.

570
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:33,079
Alright, Intelligence Team.

571
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,480
Right now, most students...

572
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:36,440
...still don't really believe it.

573
00:25:36,759 --> 00:25:37,559
Their focus is all on...

574
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:39,240
...how Guifang maintains her looks.

575
00:25:39,559 --> 00:25:40,160
To be honest...

576
00:25:41,920 --> 00:25:42,519
...I really want to know too.

577
00:25:43,519 --> 00:25:44,440
But there's a small group...

578
00:25:44,599 --> 00:25:46,200
...using this as an outlet to vent.

579
00:25:46,519 --> 00:25:48,160
Someone even started a thread on our school forum...

580
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:49,200
...specifically dedicated...

581
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:51,039
...to spreading rumors about you and your mom.

582
00:25:52,079 --> 00:25:52,799
The insults are pretty nasty.

583
00:25:55,839 --> 00:25:56,400
These...

584
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:58,559
...are all ones I tore off the bulletin board.

585
00:25:58,960 --> 00:26:00,079
They might be posted elsewhere too.

586
00:26:00,279 --> 00:26:02,079
This means the person who wants to hurt Auntie...

587
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:03,519
...is right here close to us.

588
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:05,880
So we must unite now...

589
00:26:06,039 --> 00:26:07,039
...and form an Avengers alliance.

590
00:26:07,119 --> 00:26:07,799
To protect Guifang.

591
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:08,319
Right.

592
00:26:09,559 --> 00:26:10,000
Wait a minute.

593
00:26:10,839 --> 00:26:11,240
Wait a minute.

594
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:13,920
What are you guys talking about?

595
00:26:15,559 --> 00:26:16,599
Who is whose mom?

596
00:26:17,079 --> 00:26:17,880
You didn't tell him?

597
00:26:18,799 --> 00:26:19,400
I didn't have time.

598
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:20,160
See for yourself.

599
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:21,599
Look.

600
00:26:46,559 --> 00:26:47,079
Godmother.

601
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:05,599
What Godmother?

602
00:27:08,839 --> 00:27:09,279
Hello.

603
00:27:10,519 --> 00:27:11,119
I'm Li Wai.

604
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,000
We're a perfect match.

605
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,079
Let's check our astrological compatibility later.

606
00:27:13,079 --> 00:27:14,960
How about I call you Fangfang?

607
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:15,680
As long as I'm here...

608
00:27:16,559 --> 00:27:18,160
...I won't let anything trouble you.

609
00:27:18,359 --> 00:27:19,680
My admiration for you...

610
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:21,359
...is beyond words.

611
00:27:21,759 --> 00:27:22,720
I'm going to confess to her.

612
00:27:23,359 --> 00:27:23,920
Brother-in-law.

613
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:56,319
Godmother.

614
00:28:32,039 --> 00:28:32,960
Can't count on him anymore.

615
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:35,480
I'll go ask the school if we can check the surveillance.

616
00:28:35,759 --> 00:28:36,880
See who actually posted these.

617
00:28:37,079 --> 00:28:38,039
I'll go check other places too...

618
00:28:38,039 --> 00:28:39,039
...to see if there are more posters.

619
00:28:39,359 --> 00:28:40,680
This person is really foul-mouthed.

620
00:28:41,119 --> 00:28:42,000
Watch me flame him to death.

621
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:42,920
I'll flame him.

622
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:43,359
Forget it.

623
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,400
On the internet...

624
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:46,400
...arguing with anonymous people is pointless.

625
00:28:47,039 --> 00:28:49,200
The most important thing now is to protect my mom.

626
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:50,240
Let's go.

627
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:51,440
You're right.

628
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,119
I almost acted rashly there.

629
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:54,079
Let's go.

630
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:24,519
We should act our age.

631
00:29:25,319 --> 00:29:27,200
Why do you keep trying to fit in with young people?

632
00:29:28,559 --> 00:29:29,720
You went to the amusement park...

633
00:29:30,839 --> 00:29:32,279
...and mingled with the kids.

634
00:29:33,359 --> 00:29:34,640
You even got a confession from Wei Mingtian.

635
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:36,799
Do you really think you're young now?

636
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:39,400
Do you even know who you are anymore?

637
00:30:00,279 --> 00:30:00,680
A Fu

638
00:30:01,359 --> 00:30:01,759
A Fu

639
00:30:02,279 --> 00:30:02,640
A...

640
00:30:05,279 --> 00:30:06,400
You wander around all day when nothing's up

641
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:07,359
But disappear when I actually need you

642
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:15,319
Brother Cow, Brother Cow

643
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:16,759
Do you know A Fu?

644
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,279
If you know him, tell him to find me

645
00:30:18,359 --> 00:30:18,839
Do you know him?

646
00:30:19,599 --> 00:30:21,160
A Fu, A Fu, A Fu

647
00:30:24,279 --> 00:30:24,720
Thanks

648
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:29,880
Brother Sheep

649
00:30:30,799 --> 00:30:31,680
Brother Sheep, Brother Sheep

650
00:30:32,559 --> 00:30:33,440
Do you know A Fu?

651
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:35,039
If you know him

652
00:30:35,039 --> 00:30:36,240
Tell him to hurry up and find me, okay?

653
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:36,960
Tell him to show up

654
00:30:37,279 --> 00:30:37,680
Brother Sheep

655
00:30:38,759 --> 00:30:39,079
Brother Sheep

656
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:40,960
Thanks, thanks

657
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:47,440
Brother Goose

658
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:48,319
Brother Goose

659
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:49,440
Do you know A Fu?

660
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:49,920
A Fu

661
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:51,359
Where is he? Over there?

662
00:30:51,559 --> 00:30:52,160
Brother Goose, Brother Goose

663
00:30:52,519 --> 00:30:53,519
Brother Goose, where is A Fu?

664
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:54,799
Are you two messing with me?

665
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:56,039
If you know, say something

666
00:30:56,039 --> 00:30:56,799
If you don't, say something too

667
00:30:56,799 --> 00:30:57,400
Do you know him or not?

668
00:30:58,519 --> 00:30:58,920
Big Brother

669
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:20,519
Goodbye

670
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,559
My ninth first love

671
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,359
Goodbye

672
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:34,599
Cousin

673
00:31:36,079 --> 00:31:36,599
No

674
00:31:37,880 --> 00:31:39,160
Godmother

675
00:31:42,759 --> 00:31:43,319
Godmother

676
00:31:47,599 --> 00:31:49,599
Should I let Xiaocan know?

677
00:31:51,279 --> 00:31:52,640
Is that her and her son?

678
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,720
Looks pretty immoral

679
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:55,839
Seriously

680
00:31:56,119 --> 00:31:57,319
I certainly wouldn't

681
00:31:58,359 --> 00:31:59,640
That is just too much

682
00:31:59,799 --> 00:32:02,359
Always rushing around, who knows what she's up to

683
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:07,079
It was you guys, wasn't it?

684
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,039
Auntie

685
00:32:09,799 --> 00:32:10,759
What did you say?

686
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:11,559
Yeah, what are you talking about?

687
00:32:11,559 --> 00:32:12,279
Yeah, Auntie

688
00:32:12,359 --> 00:32:13,519
I'm talking about spreading rumors

689
00:32:13,799 --> 00:32:15,559
You're the ones sending me harassing messages, right?

690
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:18,160
You chase stars until you can't tell right from wrong

691
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,640
Are you doing right by your idol?

692
00:32:19,759 --> 00:32:21,519
You have the nerve to mention our Xiaotian?

693
00:32:21,920 --> 00:32:23,160
Why don't you take a look at yourself?

694
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,519
What kind of old hag you are

695
00:32:25,519 --> 00:32:26,839
Isn't that the truth?

696
00:32:27,279 --> 00:32:28,680
Why did you hide your age?

697
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:29,759
Don't you know yourself?

698
00:32:29,960 --> 00:32:30,720
And besides

699
00:32:31,079 --> 00:32:33,279
If you dare to do it, don't be afraid of people talking

700
00:32:33,359 --> 00:32:35,279
Yeah, stop playing dumb

701
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,200
I, Kong Guifang

702
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,839
Was born in 1977

703
00:33:02,319 --> 00:33:03,279
I am 46 years old this year

704
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:08,160
This year's Tier 1 cutoff for science students

705
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,119
Was 512 points

706
00:33:11,079 --> 00:33:12,640
I scored 563 points

707
00:33:13,079 --> 00:33:15,599
And am a formally admitted student of Duxing University

708
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:19,960
Since I was seven years old

709
00:33:21,519 --> 00:33:23,039
My life's wish has been to go to college

710
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:25,599
But when I was 18

711
00:33:26,279 --> 00:33:27,519
Something happened in my family

712
00:33:28,160 --> 00:33:28,960
And I had to drop out

713
00:33:31,359 --> 00:33:33,000
Over 20 years passed in a flash

714
00:33:35,319 --> 00:33:37,039
I still feel that not going to college

715
00:33:38,519 --> 00:33:40,319
Is the biggest regret of my life

716
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:43,759
So I went to a prep school

717
00:33:43,759 --> 00:33:45,119
And studied my heart out for a year

718
00:33:46,599 --> 00:33:47,680
Just like all of you

719
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,720
I took the college entrance exam

720
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:51,559
And am standing in a university classroom now

721
00:33:53,559 --> 00:33:55,680
Yes, I look young

722
00:33:56,599 --> 00:33:57,319
I don't look my age

723
00:33:59,079 --> 00:34:00,359
But if I told everyone I met

724
00:34:01,279 --> 00:34:02,759
That I'm 46 years old

725
00:34:03,359 --> 00:34:04,480
You wouldn't be able to tell, right?

726
00:34:05,839 --> 00:34:06,680
Wouldn't you think

727
00:34:07,319 --> 00:34:09,280
I came to the school to sell cosmetics?

728
00:34:11,119 --> 00:34:12,559
Then would you still be able to

729
00:34:13,280 --> 00:34:14,559
Be as close to me as before?

730
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:26,400
College life, for me,

731
00:34:27,719 --> 00:34:29,239
is truly precious.

732
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:31,920
I've longed for it for over thirty years.

733
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:37,639
I just wanted to experience college life properly.

734
00:34:39,159 --> 00:34:40,440
I didn't want so many people focusing on

735
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,639
why I look so young.

736
00:34:43,599 --> 00:34:45,320
After all, how many people in this world

737
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,159
can fulfill a regret from their twenties

738
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,880
when they are nearly fifty?

739
00:35:01,159 --> 00:35:02,360
If my hiding the truth

740
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,440
has hurt everyone,

741
00:35:07,599 --> 00:35:08,360
then right here,

742
00:35:10,159 --> 00:35:11,840
I want to sincerely say to everyone:

743
00:35:15,159 --> 00:35:15,679
I'm sorry.

744
00:35:28,159 --> 00:35:30,440
Actually, my mom has always wanted to go to college.

745
00:35:31,119 --> 00:35:32,920
For so many years, I've known

746
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:33,960
she wasn't content.

747
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,280
Aren't we being a bit too harsh?

748
00:35:35,519 --> 00:35:36,719
She just wanted to go to college.

749
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:37,760
What's wrong with that?

750
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,840
Kong Guifang, I support you.

751
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:50,840
What is going on here?

752
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:53,480
Even if you love studying,

753
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:56,519
going to the same university as your own son,

754
00:35:56,519 --> 00:35:58,920
isn't that disgusting, Auntie?

755
00:35:59,239 --> 00:36:00,440
Exactly.

756
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,840
Me going to the same university as my son,

757
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:04,559
how is that disgusting?

758
00:36:05,159 --> 00:36:05,840
How is it not disgusting?

759
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:07,440
Aren't you the ones being disgusting?

760
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,400
Aren't you the ones saying disgusting things?

761
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:10,760
Let me tell you,

762
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,800
delete that stuff online for me.

763
00:36:13,159 --> 00:36:14,280
Or else I won't be polite.

764
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:14,920
Alright then.

765
00:36:15,519 --> 00:36:16,519
I'd like to see

766
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,199
how you won't be polite to me.

767
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:19,679
I...

768
00:36:20,199 --> 00:36:21,559
Mom, Mom, Mom.

769
00:36:21,559 --> 00:36:22,039
Stop fighting.

770
00:36:22,239 --> 00:36:22,639
Let go.

771
00:36:22,920 --> 00:36:24,000
How does this kid talk like that?

772
00:36:24,199 --> 00:36:25,960
Where is your conscience? Where did it go?

773
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,320
Kong Xiaocan.

774
00:36:29,079 --> 00:36:30,480
What is wrong with you?

775
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:32,840
Be reasonable.

776
00:36:33,079 --> 00:36:34,760
Do you have a conscience? Do you?

777
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:35,760
How can you talk like that?

778
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:36,400
Okay, okay.

779
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,039
Let go.

780
00:36:38,239 --> 00:36:39,599
Did you hear what she just said?

781
00:36:40,159 --> 00:36:41,199
She was so out of line.

782
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:42,280
Kong Xiaocan, why are you stopping me?

783
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:42,800
Enough, enough, enough.

784
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,920
I'm telling you, did you hear what she just said?

785
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:45,039
Look how old you are.

786
00:36:45,039 --> 00:36:46,760
Why are you arguing with a kid?

787
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:48,039
Look how old I am?

788
00:36:48,119 --> 00:36:48,679
Whose side are you on?

789
00:36:48,679 --> 00:36:50,039
Don't give me that "whatever" attitude.

790
00:36:50,039 --> 00:36:50,840
Enough, listen to me.

791
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:51,719
Can you be reasonable, Mom?

792
00:36:52,119 --> 00:36:52,960
Who's reasoning with you?

793
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,559
You don't understand the internet.

794
00:36:55,639 --> 00:36:57,039
The internet's memory only lasts three days.

795
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,440
In three days, everyone will focus on something else.

796
00:36:58,440 --> 00:36:59,239
And forget about this.

797
00:36:59,239 --> 00:36:59,840
Just endure it.

798
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:00,840
Can't you wait three days?

799
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:02,119
If you argue and make a scene like this,

800
00:37:02,519 --> 00:37:03,480
more and more people will pay attention.

801
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:04,840
Won't that affect your life?

802
00:37:05,159 --> 00:37:06,320
Don't be in such a rush to give your opinion.

803
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:07,480
I have more say in this matter than you.

804
00:37:07,639 --> 00:37:08,840
I've been online more than you've eaten meals.

805
00:37:10,679 --> 00:37:11,079
Mom.

806
00:37:12,159 --> 00:37:13,480
You've worked hard for most of your life.

807
00:37:14,039 --> 00:37:15,840
You finally get to live the life you want.

808
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:17,719
Can't we just live comfortably?

809
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:18,840
Don't bother with them.

810
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:21,400
Your son isn't afraid of trouble.

811
00:37:22,159 --> 00:37:22,679
But I don't want

812
00:37:22,679 --> 00:37:24,000
others to affect your current life.

813
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,039
You don't have a dad.

814
00:37:25,039 --> 00:37:26,360
Why do you sound so much like a dad?

815
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,440
I'm really doing this for your own good.

816
00:37:28,559 --> 00:37:29,280
Now it smells even stronger.

817
00:37:34,519 --> 00:37:35,719
Is that what you all think?

818
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,960
Guifang, this thing is never-ending.

819
00:37:39,119 --> 00:37:39,800
People who believe in you,

820
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,320
even if you don't say anything, we know clearly.

821
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:43,400
Those mobs, no matter how much you explain,

822
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,199
they will only believe what they want to believe.

823
00:37:45,199 --> 00:37:46,639
Who said I'm going to use my mouth?

824
00:37:46,719 --> 00:37:47,320
Then what?

825
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:48,840
You going to crawl through the internet cable and pull their hair?

826
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:49,639
Slap them in the face?

827
00:37:49,639 --> 00:37:50,519
Why can't I?

828
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:52,440
Just because we can't see them,

829
00:37:52,559 --> 00:37:53,920
does that mean they can say whatever they want

830
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:54,840
on the internet?

831
00:37:55,239 --> 00:37:56,480
You can't do that in reality,

832
00:37:56,559 --> 00:37:58,039
so why is it okay online?

833
00:37:58,679 --> 00:38:00,079
The internet is not a lawless place.

834
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,280
If they dare to say that,

835
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,880
they have to be responsible for their words.

836
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:03,599
Do you understand?

837
00:38:04,679 --> 00:38:05,039
Right.

838
00:38:07,719 --> 00:38:08,400
Godmother, Godmother.

839
00:38:09,079 --> 00:38:10,039
I support you.

840
00:38:12,159 --> 00:38:14,599
The law is indeed the most effective method.

841
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:15,920
But it will be very hard.

842
00:38:16,519 --> 00:38:17,400
Have you thought it through?

843
00:38:19,400 --> 00:38:20,159
I've made up my mind.

844
00:38:21,679 --> 00:38:22,079
Okay.

845
00:38:23,639 --> 00:38:24,519
Since you've made up your mind,

846
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:25,679
then let's just do it.

847
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:27,239
Let's go all out.

848
00:38:35,199 --> 00:38:36,119
Kong Xiaocan, are you still going to endure this?

849
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,519
If that's the case...

850
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:44,360
Endure my ass.

851
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:44,960
Don't swear.

852
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:47,840
Screw it.

853
00:38:53,199 --> 00:38:53,800
Feel free to look around.

854
00:38:55,719 --> 00:38:56,639
Everything is fresh.

855
00:39:00,559 --> 00:39:01,760
Their family's Old Kong...

856
00:39:02,719 --> 00:39:04,559
Hasn't he been paralyzed for years?

857
00:39:04,559 --> 00:39:06,400
He was fine for so long while paralyzed.

858
00:39:06,559 --> 00:39:08,400
But died just when the girl got pregnant.

859
00:39:08,719 --> 00:39:10,000
If that's not a curse, what is?

860
00:39:11,079 --> 00:39:13,039
The child in her belly is also a jerk.

861
00:39:13,159 --> 00:39:15,039
Heard she tried for years without success.

862
00:39:15,039 --> 00:39:17,079
But got pregnant the day Old Kong died.

863
00:39:17,679 --> 00:39:19,079
Exactly. So shameless.

864
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:26,840
Tolerance only encourages them to go further.

865
00:39:27,639 --> 00:39:28,559
We have to draw our swords.

866
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:31,000
Let them know we're not pushovers.

867
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:32,159
Shut up, all of you!

868
00:39:33,199 --> 00:39:34,920
Do you all have nothing better to do?

869
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:35,840
Badmouthing me right here.

870
00:39:36,199 --> 00:39:37,000
Let me tell you something.

871
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:40,320
I, Kong Guifang, haven't wronged anyone.

872
00:39:41,239 --> 00:39:42,719
Neither has the child in my belly.

873
00:39:44,679 --> 00:39:45,599
Our child...

874
00:39:46,559 --> 00:39:47,800
The due date is in June.

875
00:39:48,719 --> 00:39:50,480
You'd better all come to the full moon party then.

876
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,000
Don't any of you run away.

877
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:53,360
Also...

878
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,519
If I hear...

879
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:57,519
you badmouthing me and my child again...

880
00:39:58,159 --> 00:39:59,480
don't blame me for overturning your stall...

881
00:39:59,599 --> 00:40:00,519
and smashing your door.

882
00:40:02,079 --> 00:40:03,000
Don't blame me for getting nasty.

883
00:40:04,239 --> 00:40:06,599
This radish is over a jin.

884
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,039
Keep the change.
